HEADWORD: Enamelist
<hw>En*am"el*ist</hw>, }</mhw>
<pos>n.</pos> <def>One who enamels; a workman or artist who applies
enamels in ornamental work.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>enameller</asp>, <asp>enamellist</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Enamor</ent>⟦br⟧
